long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,el,en,en_AU,en_GB,e: Ospey is an open-source GPL compliant fork of Stylish, based on an older version before the privacy changes. It can manage custom CSS, whether from userstyles.org, or your own configurations. It is easy to install and use, and with the rare-if-any updates, you can be sure that none of your custom CSS scripts will ever be impacted.
long.de,es,fr: osprey is a fork of Stylish that can manage custom CSS from userstyles.org
